quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  21,58,"O wa…ói …ói kunte, si wanaa mawndu majji ndun, mbelejo'o kam…ďe …ďe nduttoto e mayru."
  21,59,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Ko hommbo wa…ói …óu'un e dewetee…ói amen …óin? Pellet, on ko o jeyaa…óo e too√Ī…ďe …ďen."
  21,60,"∆Āe mb'i: "Min naniino suka no jaŇčtoo …ói ko Ibraahiima o wi'etaa"."
  21,61,"∆Āe mi'i: "ngaddee mo yeeso gite yim…ďe …ďe, belejo'o …ďe ceedoto"."
  21,62,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Enee, Ibraahiima ko an wa…ói …óu'um …óoo e dewetee…ói amen …óin?""
  21,63,"O maaki: "Ko woni, ko mawndu majji ndun golle …óum, lanndee…ói si tawii …ói laatike hi…ói kaala"."
  21,64,"∆Āe nduttii fa'ade e woŇčkiiji ma…ď…ďe, …ďe mb'i: "Pellet, ko onon ngoni too√Ī…ďe …ďen"."
  21,65,"Refti …ďe nguggini ko'e ma…ď…ďe …óen […ďe mbi'i:] gooŇč…óii ha…óa anndi …ói'i wonaa layat…ói."
  21,66,"O maaki: "Enee, on ndewat gaanin Alla kon ko nafataa on hay e hu'unde lorrataa on kadi?""
  21,67,"Bis mo'on e kon ko ndewoton ga Alla. Kaa on kakkiltaa?"
  21,68,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Sunnee mo, mballee dewetee…ói mo'on …óin, si tawii ko on golloo…ďe"."
  21,69,"Min Daali: "eeyma yiite, laato …ďuu…ďol e kisal e dow Ibraahiima"."
  21,70,"∆Āe pa'andii mo pewje Min mba…ói …ďe pertube …ďen."
  21,71,"Min dan…ódi mo [Min ndan …ói kadi] Luutu fa'ade e ndin leydi ndi Min mbarkini e mu'un wonan'de tageefooji …óin."
  21,72,"Min ngkki mo Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba ka …ďeydugol, kala ma…ď…ďe Min mba…ói […ďe] mo∆ī∆īu…ďe."